<plot>Inspiration Today! is the Inspiration Networks flagship daily television program. Every weeknight, hosts David and Barbara Cerullo reach out with the powerful Word of God to touch lives and meet the needs of hurting people everywhere with the message of Christ and His love. Bringing an understanding of what it's like living with the challenges of today's world, David and Barbara reach out to viewers with the hope, peace, and joy that only God can give. The ministry of Inspiration Today! is built on the theme "We Are Here for You!" and provides personal ministry to meet viewers at their point of need.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?266472</url></doc>
